Wars like this, it's always muppets like you and I suffer. Maybe having a beer in the middle of New York and sudden a bomb goes off. Things like that, causality. Cause and effect. Nothing happens out of nowhere. Americans need to ask themselves, what did you do to the other nations? That bill will eventually come due.

